commit.message:
Makefile.in: Replace all uses of libext with libsuffix.

2007-06-01  Andrew Pinski  <andrew_pinski@playstation.sony.com>

        * Makefile.in: Replace all uses of libext with libsuffix.
        * configure.ac: Likewise.
        * configure: Regenerate.

        Revert:
        * Makefile.in: Remove all uses of $(libext).

From-SVN: r125275

files.patch:

+
+	* Makefile.in: Replace all uses of libext with libsuffix.
+	* configure.ac: Likewise.
+	* configure: Regenerate.
+
+	Revert:
+	* Makefile.in: Remove all uses of $(libext).
+

 	* Makefile.in: Remove all uses of $(libext).
